{"tid":1453360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK: 眼部受傷女子鞏膜破裂鼻骨骨折　已進行緊急手術","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:42:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a060937013bc8c2c193173e65076b7db2f7cd52d","tid":1453360,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1474123_1_L_20190812114004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1474123_1_L_20190812114004.jpg&h=b3f68c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474123-20190812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474123-20190812.htm&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=97f86565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474123-20190812.htm&h=cba91aba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474123-20190812.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀警署外昨日再有警民衝突，一名女子血流披面，倒臥地上。現場所見，她右眼腫起流血，救護員到場包紮後將她送院。有傳媒拍攝現場遺下一個被布袋彈打穿右邊外殼的眼罩，上面沾有鮮血。根據傷者入院時的消息，傷者眼球破裂，嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，根據昨晚傷者送院時所知的初步情況，她的右眼有鞏膜破裂、晶體受損、上頜骨、鼻骨有骨折。據了解傷者送院後已進行緊急手術。"},{"pid":"21db8814c8c275aa722bf3b3c673f0c84acce264","tid":1453360,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8316fb0478566ce9b9c812fe1781aa2e4c6a2665","tid":1453360,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e922c29dfdd9a1746838d4a4b381658a289103d","tid":1453360,"uid":8833,"like":1,"dislike":